lead_paragraph: Australia have named uncapped all-rounder Hilton Cartwright and thrown Glenn Maxwell a lifeline in a 14-man squad for a three-match one-day international series against New Zealand next month.

headline.print_headline: Uncapped Cartwright Named in Australia ODI Squad
